<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1021909>
    dc:description "Fig 1. Holoparasitus madridensis sp. nov., male (A-F, M), female (G-L, N). (A) Femur, genu, tibia of leg II. (B) Genital lamina. (C) Palptrochanter. (D) Corniculus. (E-N) Gnathotectum. (F) Chelicera, antiaxial view. (G) Presternal plate and sternal shield. (H) Epigynium. (I) Paragynium. (J-K) Endogynium. (L-M) Group of denticles on coxa II." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1021909/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

